{
  "id": "adv_event_2504_01_03",
  "title": "旗揚げ！劇団★見～二人のアリスとWONDERLAND～ 3話 アリスオーディション",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—The Next Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "演目は『不思議の国のアリス』で決まりとして",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ the program is settled as Alice in Wonderland‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "肝心の配役なんやけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but the important part is the casting…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "当然、アリス役は私がやりますわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Naturally‚ I’ll be playing Alice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.230000019,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "主役はスーパーアイドルの私以外あり得ませんわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There’s no way anyone but a super idol like me could be the lead.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "この劇団の座長は私……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m the leader of this troupe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.7622470538,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "アリス役は私がやる……これは譲れない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll play Alice… this is something I won’t give up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.3000021617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……さっきからずっとこんな調子で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…They’ve been like this the whole time‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.9755800247,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "話が一向にまとまらへんなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and the discussion isn’t getting anywhere.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.563403225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "すずはいつものことだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu being like this is normal‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.9986637751,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "雫がここまで強情を張るのはめずらしいわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but it’s rare to see Shizuku this stubborn.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.2967365583,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "「演劇をやりたい」って劇団★見を立ち上げたのは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan was the one who said she wanted to do theater",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.1264189083,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "雫ちゃんだからね。それだけやる気に燃えてるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and founded Troupe★Hoshimi‚ after all. She’s just that fired up.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.2300698917,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "話し合いで決めるのは難しそうやし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It looks tough to decide this by discussion alone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.7496165275,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ここは公平にオーディションしてみるのはどうやろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about holding a fair audition instead?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.063403225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "二人にアリス役を演じてもろて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll have both of you perform as Alice‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8362829844,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "うちら三人で審査して、誰にするか決めるんよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and the three of us will judge and decide who gets the role.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.5096707026,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "より多くの票を集めた方がアリス役ですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whoever gets more votes becomes Alice‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.0197521845,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "望むところですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s exactly what I want!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8000021617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "絶対に負けたくない……このオーディション……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I absolutely don’t want to lose… this audition…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.0095937092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんに勝って、アリスになるのは私……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll beat Suzu-chan and become Alice…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.2273828824,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ほな、うちが原作のワンシーンを台本に書き起こすから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright then‚ I’ll adapt one scene from the original into a script‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.9518388748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "三十分後にスタジオでオーディション開始や",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and we’ll start the audition in the studio in thirty minutes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.3666460675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――三十分後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Thirty Minutes Later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.5961017609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "「あれは……うさぎが喋りながら走ってる……？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“That is… a rabbit running while talking…?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5961037954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "ダメ……もっと大きな声で感情を込めて言わないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… I need to say it louder‚ with more emotion…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.8666688283,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5354.965782299999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "雫ちゃん、もうすぐオーディションの時間やけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Shizuku-chan‚ the audition’s about to start.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.138847224,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "調子はどないですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How are you feeling?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.2216346106,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "調子は、良くない……大声を出すのは苦手で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not great… I’m bad at raising my voice…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.1792329152,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "セリフに感情を込めるのも、難しい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And putting emotion into lines is hard…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.1775626428,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "セリフに気持ちを乗せるのって結構難しいんよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Conveying emotion through lines is pretty hard‚ yeah.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.6766895611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "うちもそれで苦労したから、気持ちは分かります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I struggled with that too‚ so I know how you feel.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1113360088,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "「あれは！　うさぎが喋りながら走ってる！？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "“That is! A rabbit running while talking!?”",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.2524720191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "向こうですずちゃんも練習してはるなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looks like Suzu-chan’s practicing over there too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.8919507662,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんらしい、気持ちのこもった大きな声やわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That big‚ heartfelt voice is so like her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.0230595272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "分かる……迷いがなくて、思い切りがいいから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know… there’s no hesitation‚ she commits fully…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.3297738074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03/sud_vo_adv_event_2504_01_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "聞いてて気持ちいい……あれは私には真似出来ない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It feels good just listening… I can’t imitate that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.5999986012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
